                    <span>This book had a good overview of lighting techniques and ideas; however, all the examples and photos were of homes decorated in a very modern style, not applicable to most people.  The same principles employed in Craftsman, western, or other home styles would have been useful.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Very Good, but no measurements</div>
